1. Cach can giua noi dung trong khoi
  - Cach 1: width + height + line-height + tac
  - Cach 2: width + height + flex + align-items +justify-content +tac(block)
  - Cach 3: them padding 

 2. Position:
 - absolute: dua the den 1 vi tri bat ki tren trang   
 - relative: Vi tri tuong doi, ko phu thuoc vao doi tương nao ben ngoai ca
 - fixed: set vi tri co dinh theo man hinh
